pdate-delete-deployment/README.md`, which explains the deployment workflow and how to run the example\\n   - The main `client-go--v0.32.0/README.md` provides overall client library documentation and explains that code development occurs in `kubernetes/kubernetes/staging/src/k8s.io/api` and `kubernetes/kubernetes/staging/src/k8s.io/client-go`\\n\\nKey pattern insight: The Deployment struct in the API repo is the single source of truth, and the client-go example demonstrates the recommended pattern of using `retry.RetryOnConflict()` when updating to handle concurrent modifications, which is the canonical approach for managing Kubernetes resources safely.\"\n}\n",
